---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="DUI / DWI Education">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-6) 0;">
    
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumbs" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">
      <a href="/">Home</a> &gt; <a href="/programs/">Programs</a> &gt; <span aria-current="page">DUI / DWI Education</span>
    </nav>
    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue);">DUI / DWI Education</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">State-certified educational programs focusing on awareness, prevention, and legal fulfillment.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--spacing-6);">
      <div class="main-content">
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>What the Service Is</h2>
          <p>A structured psychoeducational program tailored to outline the risks of impaired driving. The course explores personal accountability, the physiological impacts of alcohol and substances, and strategies to prevent impaired driving recurrence.</p>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>Who It Is For</h2>
          <p>This program is designed for individuals who have received a DUI/DWI citation or conviction and have been ordered by the court or the MVA to complete a certified 12-hour or 26-hour education program.</p>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>How to Qualify</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Documented requirement via court order, MVA directive, or attorney recommendation.</li>
            <li>Completion of our initial substance abuse assessment.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>What Happens Next</h2>
          <p>Once you complete your intake application, our team will process it within <strong>3 business days</strong> and evaluate your case. We then assign you to upcoming class dates. Upon completion, we provide all required certifications of completion directly to your requesting agency.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
      <aside>
        <div class="card" style="background-color: var(--color-bg-offset); border-top: 4px solid var(--color-accent-gold);">
          <h3>Take the First Step</h3>
          <a href="/intake/start/" class="btn" style="display: block; width: 100%; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">Start Your Intake</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
